title: UAE weather forecast: Morning mist, humidity and rain expected this week
summary_full: UAE residents should prepare for humid mornings and increasing cloud cover this week.  Rain is possible, particularly over islands and coastal areas from Saturday night into Sunday, with another chance on Tuesday. Temperatures will rise until Monday before a slight dip.  Light to moderate winds are expected, with occasional rough seas.
